-- Isbank of Turkey to Buy Russia's Bank Sofia for $50 Million, Milliyet Says
-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 2010-10-05T05:16:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/isbank-of-turkey-to-buy-russia-s-bank-sofia-for-50-million-milliyet-says.html
Turkiye Is Bankasi  AS, Turkey’s
biggest listed bank by assets, will buy Moscow-based Bank Sofia,
Milliyet reported.  Isbank will buy the bank, with two branches in Moscow and
others in St. Petersburg, Saratov and Balakovo for about $50
million, the Istanbul-based newspaper said citing banking
sources it didn’t identify.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
